        .thumbnail
          img(src="http://images01.olx.in/ui/18/18/39/1377923469_541240939_1-Pictures-of--Channapatna-wooden-horse-for-sale.jpg", alt="Horse")
          .caption
            h3 A horse that rocks
            p The simplest way to make my daughter spend
              | some quite time, or eat her fruits.  Built to
              | last, unlink those plastic toys you have.
            p.text-success
              strong Suitable for 1-2 years, JP Nagar
