        .thumbnail
          img(src="http://i01.i.aliimg.com/wsphoto/v0/749350811/Tiger-violin-child-orgatron-educational-toys-violin-cartoon-music-piano-infant-electronic-piano-toy.jpg", alt="Piano")
          .caption
            h3 What Mozart used
            p A classical toy that never goes out of style.
              | The piano I has 4 built in tunes and 15 keys.
              | The tunes feature classical Mozart and Beethoven
            p.text-success
              strong Suitable for 1-2 years, Koramangala
